title: SF Housing Authority Properties, San Francisco, 2008
name: SF Housing Authority Properties, San Francisco, 2008
description:
SF Housing Authority Properties.  Layer created from join of Citylots layer and detailed Lot information used in the Real Estate Information System application.  Data gathered from Assessor and City Planning databases; one-to-one join with City Lots spatial layer.  Not all fields are populated.

Provides detailed ownership and other information for use in analysis for SF Housing Authority-owned properties.
